            <title>[PIG-5455] Upgrade Hadoop to 3.3.6 and Tez to 0.10.3</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PIG-5455</link>
                <project id="12310730" key="PIG">Pig</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Latest Tez (0.10.3 and later) requires Hadoop 3.3 or later &lt;br/&gt;
and simple upgrade of Hadoop failing the tests with&#160;&lt;br/&gt;
&quot;Implementing class java.lang.IncompatibleClassChangeError: Implementing class&quot;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
